{"tid":1753821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動］今晚十八區勝利巡遊","createTime":"2019-11-25T04:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T08:40:14.000Z","uid":69608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fd572ce2f615d620c8442c0f95a4242ebe34e587","tid":1753821,"uid":69608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:40:46.000Z","msg":"今次區議會險勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝勇武同和理非無割蓆<br />\n雖然可能區議會作用無咁大，但反映出來既意義其實好深遠<br />\n先唔講我地大巴大巴咁打落班民意撚到<br />\n更加代表大部分香港人政治醒覺，肯行多步去對抗建制，同時願意用選票去表態，將來普選都形式都一樣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗慶祝呢個階段勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚大家食完飯落街散步，行過建制派事務處時，不妨播下歌，飲下野，鼓舞下士氣。製造歌舞昇平環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比大家睇到我地唔係小數派<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地仲有好長路要行，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cd598e9c1ff6b94c551dafcc219fa1f2e56a68","tid":1753821,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f481c63142c0c9c50931ea13981ddff634d109","tid":1753821,"uid":69608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:41:31.000Z","msg":"琴晚太夜無嗌，好撚想慶祝呀"},{"pid":"3a93f858bc4e0d20a42cf4846b46879fc28de45c","tid":1753821,"uid":69608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f649d32286b5494bcf6c0f04a1a8ffee3cfd093a","tid":1753821,"uid":69608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass